{"tid":744453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[世界盃決賽] 克羅地亞對法國實力分析","createTime":"2018-07-16T02:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T10:29:56.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37288ae0ff616a6d6df4fe473e885441cff42147","tid":744453,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T02:55:32.000Z","msg":"寡人認為克羅地亞雖然一路過關斬將黎到決賽係好勁<br />\n但對住傳統強國法國依然係毫無招架之力<br />\n加上前幾場克羅地亞都係險勝<br />\n無法國贏得咁輕鬆<br />\n再者 法國隊整體比較年輕力壯<br />\n但今屆興爆冷 我覺得賽果應該出人意料<br />\n<br />\n所以寡人估最終法國4:2贏克羅地亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其中有粒好可能係烏龍波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373abe0d42fc3d10d213a1b3a8d352e3d5276882","tid":744453,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d374ece5c405b0fe35d3e2d27517703eebd7a0cb","tid":744453,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"負評係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f17ca76f2b767494e30651cbce3624960440fa","tid":744453,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76bc8e05134f598db94a7f31532615bdcc556a6","tid":744453,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}